            <p><lb/> דכיר <lb/> לטב קורים <lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="line"/><lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>עיי ניח נפש <lb/> בר אוכסנטים <lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
               <lb/> ליקרה דבני <supplied reason="omitted">י</supplied>שראל <lb/> שלום </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="mari0004.translation"
              corresp="#mari0004.transcription">
            <p> Be remembered With a blessing the Lord ... peace upon his soul The son of
                    Auxentios Who built (or bought) this column In honor of the Children of Israel
                    Peace.</p>
         </div>
